                                                        <p class="vs-portfolio-heading-desccription">Dooskarting is a Saudi Arabia company that offers electronic kart racing to their customers. They are part of Osool Entertainment, the pioneer in entertainment activities in Saudi Arabian region. This app is developed to allow customers to book kart race tickets, order food items and track their race results. The results are directly integrated through the IOT sensors, and as soon as the race is over, users can track their position on the app itself. Region</p>

