                                                                <h3 class="vs-portfolio-title"><span>Revv - Ride Sharing App</span>
                                                                </h3>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <p class="vs-portfolio-heading-desccription">Revv is a self-drive car rental and subscription app based in India. Within the Revv app, users get a wide range of cars to choose from and can book cars for hourly, daily, weekly, or monthly periods. Revv delivers cars to the user&#039;s doorstep and offers flexible pricing plans.</p>

