                                                        <p class="vs-portfolio-heading-desccription">InstaShop is a popular grocery delivery app that allows users to order groceries and have them delivered to their doorstep. Users can browse through a wide selection of products from various stores, add items to their cart, and schedule a delivery time that is convenient for them.</p>

