                                                        <p class="vs-portfolio-heading-desccription">FanDuel is a popular fantasy sports app that allows users to compete in daily and weekly fantasy sports contests for real money prizes. Users can create their own fantasy teams by selecting players from various professional sports leagues and compete against other users to win cash prizes.</p>

