                                                        <p class="vs-portfolio-heading-desccription">Taimi is a dating and social networking app for LGBTQ+ individuals. It is designed to provide a safe and inclusive space for people to connect, chat, and meet new friends or potential romantic partners. The app also offers features such as video calls, stories, and groups to help users interact and engage with each other.</p>

